---
// Bottom-of-main prompt-styled search input. Click or Cmd+K triggers SearchOverlay.
---

<div class="search-bar shrink-0 px-4 lg:px-6 pt-3 pb-4 bg-bg">
	<button
		type="button"
		id="searchbar-trigger"
		class="w-full flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-elevated text-fg-muted hover:bg-surface hover:border-surface-hover transition-colors text-left text-sm cursor-pointer"
		aria-label="Search posts"
	>
		<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-fg-dim" aria-hidden="true">
			<path d="M3 7a4 4 0 1 0 8 0 4 4 0 1 0-8 0M13 13l-3-3" />
		</svg>
		<span class="flex-1 text-fg-dim">Search posts or type / for commands</span>
		<kbd class="hidden sm:inline-block text-xs text-fg-dim border border-border rounded px-1.5 py-px font-mono">⌘K</kbd>
	</button>
</div>
